name: vertica-python
raw_recipe:
{%set name = "vertica-python" %}
{%set version = "0.6.14" %}
{%set compress_type = "tar.gz" %}
{%set hash_type = "sha256" %}
{%set hash_val = "595aa85b03873cbbd31dfef615e88f6239ffe1925e90bf27fb346a2d4d8df1c0" %}
{%set build_num = "0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.{{ compress_type }}
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.{{ compress_type }}
  {{ hash_type }}: {{ hash_val }}

build:
  number: {{ build_num }}
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python
    - python-dateutil >=1.5
    - pytz
    - future
    - six >=1.10.0
    - psycopg2 >=2.5.1

test:
  imports:
    - vertica_python
    - vertica_python.tests
    - vertica_python.vertica
    - vertica_python.vertica.messages
    - vertica_python.vertica.messages.backend_messages
    - vertica_python.vertica.messages.frontend_messages

about:
  home: https://github.com/uber/vertica-python/
  license_file: LICENSE
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  summary: A native Python client for the Vertica database.
  dev_url: https://github.com/uber/vertica-python/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pmlandwehr

about.summary: A native Python client for the Vertica database.
